Feline2::

She felt his hand in hers and smiled. 

Then she heard his reply to the transmission. "Shall I join you?"



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, RoboRick007 <rfa007@h...> wrote:
> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> He took her hand.
> "Yes, I love you more than anything I have ever loved," he said, 
trying
> to be as romatic as he could.
> 
> Ultra Magnus came over the comm. Hot Rod's face went into shock.
> His old friend was alive! He had had 3 mentors as a young Autobot:
> Prime, Kup, and Magnus. After he took command as Rodimus Prime, 
Magnus
> was his most trusted advisor, and second in command. He decided to 
act
> good.
> "I'll come to you, Magnus. Where are you?"
